  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the grill to medium high heat.",
    "Season the monkfish fillets with salt, black pepper, and paprika.",
    "In a small bowl, mix together lemon juice, olive oil, garlic, and dill.",
    "Brush the mixture on both sides of the monkfish fillets.",
    "Grill the monkfish for 4 minutes per side or until cooked through.",
    "Serve the monkfish in a molcajete with additional lemon wedges on the side.",
    "Garnish with chopped fresh dill and serve immediately.",
    "Make sure to handle the monkfish gently to avoid breaking the delicate flesh."
